### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "devadmin@example.com",
  "password": "DevAdmin123!"
}

### Refresh
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Get Profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Modules
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me/modules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Roles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Boards
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/kanban/boards
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Board Details
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/kanban/boards/{{boardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/kanban/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Task from HTTP",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "boardId": "{{boardId}}",
  "boardColumnId": "{{boardColumnId}}"
}

### Move Task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/kanban/tasks/{{taskId}}/move
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "boardColumnId": "{{targetColumnId}}"
}

### Comment Task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/kanban/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Progress update"
}
